	<center>
		<h1>Timestamp spoofing</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
	<p>Exported transcripts can be modified by the user, it would be nice if we could check the validity of transcripts</p>
        <p>Possible remedy</p>
	<ul>
            <li>Arbitrated solution with the VC server acting as arbitrator</li>
            <li>VC server can enter transcripts into arbitrated timestamp database automatically</li>
	</ul>
